Shelve		KEY:Shelve ~ Paper Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural						DESC:A paper drake can fold itself into a small form perfect for hiding on bookshelves and in libraries. This requires a standard action and the drake must be adjacent to papers or books large enough to contain it. While merged with the material, the paper drake cannot see its surroundings but can hear nearby sounds. Any damage dealt to the mass of paper damages both the material and the drake. A paper drake can end this effect as a free action.								SOURCEPAGE:pg.41
Tail Snap		KEY:Tail Snap ~ Paper Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	DEFINE:TailSnapDC|10+HD/2+CON	DESC:You can quickly strike with your tail, creating a loud boom. With a successfully hit upon an opponent with your tail snap attack, those struck must succeed on a DC %1 Fort save or be stunned for one round.|TailSnapDC																																														SOURCEPAGE:pg.41
Unfold		KEY:Unfold ~ Paper Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural						DESC:A paper drake can manipulate its body, allowing the creature to fold itself to change its size and shape. As a standard action, the drake can adjust its size by one step in either direction, from Small to Tiny or Small to Medium size. All normal numerical adjustments apply.																													TEMPLATE:Unfold (Enlarge)|Unfold (Reduce)	SOURCEPAGE:pg.41

