Prismatic Field	KEY:Prismatic Field ~ Prismatic Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:A scintillating field surrounds the prismatic drake. As a standard action, it forms a multi-colored sphere around itself with the defensive capabilities of the first 6 layers of prismatic wall and the offensive capabilities of the first 4 layers. Each layer may be negated as outlined in the prismatic wall spell. If a layer is negated, the drake can replace the layer after 4 rounds as a standard action.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.43

