Change Shape	KEY:Change Shape ~ River Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:You can take any animal or humanoid form three times per day as if using polymorph. A river drake usually chooses animal forms that allow the creature to go unnoticed around humanoids, such as a cat or a crow. It rarely takes humanoid form longer than necessary.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.44

