Sludge Walk		KEY:Sludge Walk ~ Sewer Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural								DESC:As a standard action, you can transform into a sludge-like form and slip through cracks, holes, or other extremely small openings. The drake retains its normal movement modes but can only move 10 ft. per round. In this form, the drake's Dexterity score drops to 5 in this form (reducing its AC to 15), it is not subject to critical hits or precision damage, and it gains a +20 bonus to Escape Artist checks to escape a grapple. The sewer drake reverts to its normal form if killed or knocked unconscious. A sewer drake can remain in this form for a number of rounds equal to 10 plus its Constitution bonus.								SOURCEPAGE:pg.45
