###Block: Song Drake abilities
# Ability Name	Unique Key				Category of Ability		Type						Define				Description																																																																																	Modify VAR					Source Page
Alter Mood		KEY:Alter Mood ~ Song Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DEFINE:AlterMoodRounds|0	DESC:You comfort friends and confuses foes. You must choose to benefit its companions or hinder its enemies. As a standard action, you begin humming a tune with an effect similar to a bard�s bardic performance class ability. This grants a +1 bonus or -1 penalty to attacks, damage, and skill checks. You can maintain this ability as a free action each following round. You can use this special ability a total number of %1 rounds. This is a sonic-based mind-affecting effect.|AlterMoodRounds	BONUS:VAR|AlterMoodRounds|CHASCORE	SOURCEPAGE:pg.46
