###Block: Steam Drake abilities
# Ability Name	Unique Key				Category of Ability		Type						Description																																																																																																Source Page
Steam Form		KEY:Steam Form ~ Steam Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:You can, as a standard action three times per day, change into a cloud of steam. This form resembles the effects of a gaseous form spell, but with a few changes. The drake can move at its normal fly speed while in steam form. Any creature occupying the same square as a steam drake in steam form suffers 1d6 fire damage. Finally, a steam drake in steam form can use its breath weapon twice as quickly (minimum 1 per round). A steam drake can maintain steam form for a number of rounds equal to its Constitution modifier and can return to its normal form as a free action.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.47

